		   if container.getLock() and container == self then
     local clone = object.clone({position = {0,100,0}})
		        function coPause()
			            coroutine.yield(0)
			            container.putObject(clone)
			            return 1
        end
		    startLuaCoroutine(self, 'coPause')
    end	
	end
